---
// Experience section component with timeline
---

<section id="experience" class="section experience-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">Mi Educacion Academica</h2>
    
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-card glass-effect">
            <div class="timeline-header">
              <h3 class="timeline-title">Tecnico en Programacion</h3>
              <span class="timeline-company">Cetis 78</span>
              <span class="timeline-date">2020 - 2023 </span>
            </div>
            <p class="timeline-description">
              Durante mi formación como Técnico en Programación adquirí las bases necesarias para desenvolverme 
              en el desarrollo de proyectos tecnológicos. Este proceso me permitió fortalecer mis habilidades 
              de análisis, resolver problemas de manera creativa y trabajar en equipo para alcanzar objetivos comunes.
            </p>
            <div class="timeline-skills">
              <span class="skill-tag">Java</span>
              <span class="skill-tag">mysql</span>
              <span class="skill-tag">python</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="timeline-marker">
          <div class="marker-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="timeline-content">
          <div class="timeline-card glass-effect">
            <div class="timeline-header">
              <h3 class="timeline-title">Ingeniero en sistemas computacionales</h3>
              <span class="timeline-company">Universsidad Autonoma de Tamaulipas (UAT)</span>
              <span class="timeline-date">2023 - Actualidad</span>
            </div>
            <p class="timeline-description">
            Diseño y desarrollo de aplicaciones y sistemas.
            Manejo de bases de datos y estructuras de información.
            Aplicación de principios de programación y algoritmos.
            Resolución de problemas mediante el uso de la tecnología.
            Trabajo en equipo para el desarrollo de proyectos.
            </p>
            <div class="timeline-skills">
              <span class="skill-tag">lynx</span>
              <span class="skill-tag">Java</span>
              <span class="skill-tag">sql-mysql</span>
              <span class="skill-tag">laravel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .experience-section {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(26, 26, 46, 0.8) 0%,
      rgba(15, 15, 35, 0.9) 100%
    );
  }

  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--gradient-bg);
    transform: translateX(-50%);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content {
    margin-left: 0;
    margin-right: calc(50% + 30px);
    text-align: right;
  }

  .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
    margin-left: calc(50% + 30px);
    margin-right: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    top: 20px;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .marker-dot {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    background: var(--gradient-bg);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 4px solid var(--dark-bg);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
    animation: markerPulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes markerPulse {
    0%, 100% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.5);
    }
    50% {
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.8);
    }
  }

  .timeline-content {
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .timeline-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.05),
      transparent
    );
    transition: left 0.5s ease;
  }

  .timeline-card:hover::before {
    left: 100%;
  }

  .timeline-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    border-color: var(--primary-purple);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
  }

  .timeline-header {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .timeline-title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-company {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--primary-purple);
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .timeline-date {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .timeline-description {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-achievements {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-achievements ul {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-achievements li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .timeline-achievements li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-pink);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .timeline-skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .skill-tag {
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .skill-tag:hover {
    background: var(--primary-purple);
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  /* Mobile Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline::before {
      left: 20px;
    }

    .timeline-item:nth-child(odd) .timeline-content,
    .timeline-item:nth-child(even) .timeline-content {
      margin-left: 50px;
      margin-right: 0;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .timeline-marker {
      left: 20px;
      transform: none;
    }

    .timeline-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-title {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .timeline-company {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .timeline-skills {
      justify-content: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .timeline-card {
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .timeline-title {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .timeline-description {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .timeline-achievements li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .skill-tag {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
